jade.tools.ascml.repository.loader
Class ModelIndex

java.lang.Object
  jade.tools.ascml.repository.loader.ModelIndex

public class ModelIndex
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds information about all models available. This means if a model is loaded it's source path is stored here or if an autoSearch is started all model-sources, that are found are also stored here. By convention files are named 'MyAgent.agent.xml' and 'MySociety.society.xml'. todo: fix the model table?! what kind of mapping is done? filename->jarfilename?
